WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:02.000
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.480
How to make an International Payment

3
00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:08.640
It's easy to make an international payment
with Online Banking.

4
00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:11.640
Making sure you have a PINsentry device to hand,

5
00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:14.760
start by clicking 'Move money'
from the homepage.

6
00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.600
Next, click 'International payment'.

7
00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:21.040
Then select the account you'd like to make
the payment from

8
00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:26.000
and enter the amount you're sending in pounds.

9
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:29.720
Select the recipient's currency
from the drop-down menu

10
00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:32.160
and you'll see the amount they will receive here.

11
00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:34.040
Click on 'Continue'.

12
00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:38.840
You can now choose whether you're paying
someone you've paid before or someone new.

13
00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:42.800
If you're paying someone new,
enter the recipient's name here.

14
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:47.040
Next, select your recipient's country
from the drop-down menu

15
00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:50.880
and enter their IBAN so we can identify
their bank account.

16
00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:54.360
Add a reference that will appear on your
bank statement

17
00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:56.640
and a reference
that will appear on theirs

18
00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:58.680
before clicking on 'Continue'.

19
00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:01.720
Now choose when you'd like to send the payment

20
00:01:01.720 --> 00:01:06.320
and let us know which account
you'd like to use to pay any applicable charges

21
00:01:06.520 --> 00:01:08.440
before clicking 'Continue'.

22
00:01:08.760 --> 00:01:11.880
Scroll down and check all the details are correct.

23
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.680
You'll now need your mobile to hand.

24
00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:19.840
Open the Barclays app and from the login
screen, tap 'Mobile PINsentry.

25
00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:23.960
Press 'Respond' and enter
your 5-digit passcode.

26
00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:29.640
Then enter the 8- digit code displayed
on your mobile here and click on 'Confirm'.

27
00:01:29.720 --> 00:01:32.360
You have 90 seconds to authorise
your payment

28
00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:36.000
with either your mobile
PINsentry or physical PINsentry.

29
00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.280
If the 90 seconds runs out, don't worry,

30
00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:44.600
just click 'Get a new rate' and you'll be able to
enter your PINsentry code again

31
00:01:44.600 --> 00:01:45.720
And you're all done.

